testcase.name: Gmail Login test_2
testcase.preconditions: Testing Gmail Login Functionality with Valid userid and incorrect password

step.actions: Type Valid gmail id in mail id section.

step.expectedresults: One webpage which gives an option to enter password.
Failed login. Message appears: password is incorrect. Try again or click : "forgot your password?" to reset it.
Sending a notification to the phone number connected to the gmail account

step.actions: Click on the login notification on my mobilephone.

Click on Yes, it's me on my mobile.

I confirm that I am the one trying to recover the password to my gmail account.
